/bird.person666</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hNeBYQN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Rammsteinstochter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>True stories from a professor</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/t9wKTIO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4J2oeMN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I've been teaching for 15 years and most students are great, but some of the nonsense I've seen is hilarious</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/83LC7OK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This one kills me (has happened multiple times)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/F2AcNrQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Clearly</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Tvqr638.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Asks if there's any "extra credit" ... me: but you didn't do any of the regular credit!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GV6QgmJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>from a long time ago when we still accepted paper assignments...  like 2008</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3GTjphG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"That's not how any of this works" meme</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zy7Fob4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Happens way more than you'd think...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9mJFSxu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's like mathematical impossible for you to pass but go ahead ... knock yourself out</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yaNSLgg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nope. Nothing we do here is "important"</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1idc1IF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>True story. Baffling. Like ever couple of weeks she'd ask again. Like some momento shit</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O2coyum.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You all know. It's always ....</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/INFGpge.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's like... you live here, it gets cold, how</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kYMvc0Z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Dog tax. This is Stash. She loves the snow

MOST VIRAL EDIT: I made all of these memes while my students took an exam. Its nice that genuine OC can still rise up from usersub around here!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/t9wKTIO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[slightskew]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Who else but the scientist himself!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/eAx5RAs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XFzfRXu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#spiderman #marvel #movies_and tv #movies</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/eAx5RAs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[NeoIsJohnWick]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>but why?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/r6BzIJn</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zwQbdHE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/r6BzIJn</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[shelworth]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Alabama: Where The Onion Is Real</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vd4ks08</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fPsZrth.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/warondumb/status/1489250541158821900?s=21</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/E7pdaE9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/warondumb/status/1489253241552465925?s=21</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vd4ks08</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[roanhouse]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Great fun</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Yv5OTjU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/d6PnhOs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Yv5OTjU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Joyika]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>One o