creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wrtO6Hh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o9WKFju.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wrtO6Hh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AkitakaL]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Target acquired</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MQQTS60</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TkSeDhq.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You might have done some extended Target browsing yourself, either accidentally or even on purpose, and wondered why they just let you walk out.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LDvVLPA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>From the source itself: https://corporate.target.com/article/2012/02/an-unexpected-career-target-forensic-services-labo</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SoBUaiB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's because they're one of the top crime labs in the country. They got you, your vehicle, probably even how you walk on file.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XZk4BAI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HQwtNww.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is for NYS, but you get the idea (not sure from where the woman from #1 hails, but the amounts line up pretty well): https://www.nysenate.gov/legislation/laws/PEN/155.35</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZOsZqzK.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So, in New York, as is our example because of the amount, the maximum punishment is 7 years, but as long as you didn't resist the arrest and have no priors, it'll probably be as low as 1 year probation. https://www.nysenate.gov/legislation/laws/PEN/70.00

The point is, check your local jurisdiction.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XskHrCz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/MQQTS60</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jansenart]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Posting weird stuff</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Y48IDba</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/K61BcwF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Y48IDba</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DrakonRax]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nothing to see here</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RHTUxDo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zHHZPOv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RHTUxDo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Threefall]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>